-- Merkel Ally Kauder Sees Spain Convincing Markets, Passauer Says
-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 2012-04-20T00:01:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/merkel-ally-kauder-sees-spain-convincing-markets-passauer-says.html
Spain is carrying out ambitious
reforms that will convince investors concerned about the
country’s finances,  Volker Kauder , a senior lawmaker in German
Chancellor Angela Merkel’s party, was quoted as saying by the
 Passauer Neue Presse .  Politicians should stay calm and shouldn’t let markets
pressure them, Kauder, the Christian Democratic bloc’s floor
leader in the German parliament, was quoted as saying by the
Passau, Germany-based newspaper today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony Czuczka in Berlin at 
